Enum Class ParkingAreaAmenities

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<ParkingAreaAmenities>
us.mn.state.dot.tms.ParkingAreaAmenities
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<ParkingAreaAmenities>, Constable
public enum ParkingAreaAmenities extends Enum<ParkingAreaAmenities>
Amenities enumeration for parking areas. The ordinal values correspond to the bits in the iris.parking_area_amenities look-up table.
Author:
Douglas Lau
